spirent.methodology.VerifyDbQueryCommand.SqlQuery: SELECT TxRes.FrameCount-RxRes.FrameCount AS 'FL Count', CAST(TxRes.FrameCount-RxRes.FrameCount AS FLOAT)/TxRes.FrameCount AS 'FLR', MinLatency*1e3 AS 'Min FTD (ms)', ROUND(AvgLatency*1e3,3) AS 'Mean FTD (ms)', MaxLatency*1e3 AS 'Max FTD (ms)', MinJitter*1e3 AS 'Min FDV (ms)', ROUND(AvgJitter*1e3,3) AS 'Mean FDV (ms)', MaxJitter*1e3 AS 'Max FDV (ms)', OutSeqFrameCount AS 'Out of Sequence Frame Count', LateFrameCount AS 'Late Frame Count' FROM TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes INNER JOIN RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes ON TxRes.ParentStreamBlock = RxRes.ParentStreamBlock INNER JOIN RelationTable ON SourceHnd = RxRes.ParentStreamBlock INNER JOIN Tag ON Tag.Handle = TargetHnd WHERE Tag.Name = 'CurrStream'
